; Regression test for issue #792: Adjustment in ledger register report with -Mn (BZ#792)
; https://github.com/ledger/ledger/issues/792
;
; When using -Mn (--monthly --collapse), the register report should correctly
; collapse multiple transactions per month into a single line. With a single
; account, it should show the account name; with multiple accounts collapsed
; together, it shows <Total>.

2013/01/05 Buy groceries
    Expenses:Food     $50.00
    Assets:Cash

2013/01/20 Dining out
    Expenses:Dining   $30.00
    Assets:Cash

2013/02/05 Buy groceries
    Expenses:Food     $40.00
    Assets:Cash

test reg -Mn Expenses
13-Jan-01 - 13-Jan-31           <Total>                      $80.00       $80.00
13-Feb-01 - 13-Feb-28           Expenses:Food                $40.00      $120.00
end test
